Code preview of table SOURCE

if exists (select 1
from sys.sysreferences r join sys.sysobjects o on (o.id = r.constid and o.type = 'F')
where r.fkeyid = object_id('METADATA') and o.name = 'FK_UNITS_PROCCESS_SOURCES')
alter table METADATA
drop constraint FK_UNITS_PROCCESS_SOURCES
go

if exists (select 1
from sys.sysreferences r join sys.sysobjects o on (o.id = r.constid and o.type = 'F')
where r.fkeyid = object_id('PARAMETER') and o.name = 'FK_PARAMETE_REFERENCE_SOURCE')
alter table PARAMETER
drop constraint FK_PARAMETE_REFERENCE_SOURCE
go

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('SOURCE')
and type = 'U')
drop table SOURCE
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: SOURCE */
/*==============================================================*/
create table SOURCE (
SOURCE varchar(20) not null,
"GROUP" varchar(20) null,
NAME varchar(100) not null,
TYPESOURCE varchar(100) null,
FILENAME varchar(100) null,
PATH varchar(500) null,
CODINGFORMAT varchar(100) null,
HEADER varchar(20) null default 'N/A'
constraint CKC_HEADER_SOURCE check (HEADER is null or (HEADER in ('N/A','YES','NO'))),
DELIMITER varchar(10) null,
LEFT_ENCLOSURE varchar(10) null,
RIGHT_ENCLOUSURE varchar(10) null,
SHEET_NAME varchar(50) null,
JRXMLPATH varchar(500) null,
DATASOURCE varchar(20) null,
SQL varchar(Max) null,
DATASOURCEPARENT varchar(20) null,
SQLPARENT varchar(Max) null,
constraint PK_SOURCE primary key nonclustered (SOURCE)
)
go
